    "title": "Mtumishi wa Mungu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "mtumishi wa mungu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kwenye <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:1-Isa66:24\">Isaya 40–66</a>, mtumishi wa Mungu ni muhimu sana na anaonekana mara nyingi. Mtumishi huyu anatangaza mpangilio mpya wa haki na uadilifu kwa ulimwengu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:3-Isa42:4\">42:3–4</a>). Anauandaa ulimwengu kwa ajili ya kuja kwa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">52:7</a>).</p><p>Nani ni mtumishi wa Bwana? Isaya anamuelezea mtumishi kama &quot;Israeli,&quot; ambaye inatenda kama shahidi wa Mungu na &quot;nuru&quot; kwa mataifa mengine (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:8\">Isaya 41:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:1-Isa44:2\">44:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:10\">43:10</a>). Hata hivyo, taifa la Israeli halikuweza kutimiza kikamilifu misheni hii kwa sababu lilikuwa kiziwi na kipofu kiroho, na lilihitaji msamaha wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:19\">42:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:21-Isa44:22\">44:21–22</a>). Israeli ilishindwa mara kwa mara.</p><p>Kinyume chake, mtumishi wa Mungu ni mwaminifu na anasubiri ukombozi (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:3\">Isaya 61:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:1-Isa62:5\">62:1–5</a>). Mtumishi huyu anawakilisha watu wacha Mungu katika Israeli. Mtumishi ni shahidi mwaminifu wa Mungu kwa wanadamu na anapinga desturi za kipagani za dini za sanamu.</p><p>Nabii Isaya anamwelezea mtumishi kama mtiifu na anayeteseka. Yesu Kristo alitimiza dhana ya &quot;mtumishi anayeteseka.&quot; Alikuwa Mwisraeli ambaye alikuwa mwaminifu kikamilifu na aliteseka kwa ajili ya wengine. Kupitia mateso yake, baraka za Mungu zilifikia wengi, ikiwa ni pamoja na mataifa mengine (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:22-Acts26:23\">Matendo 26:22–23</a>).</p><p>Wakiwa wameungana na Kristo, mitume walishiriki ujumbe wa Mungu kama watumishi wa Mungu kwa Wayahudi na watu wa mataifa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:47\">Matendo 13:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:14-Acts26:18\">26:14–18</a>). Wote wanaomwamini Yesu wanashiriki katika utume wa &quot;mtumishi.&quot; Wanatenda kama watumishi wa Mungu duniani (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:7\">Wakolosai 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12\">4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:6\">1 Timotheo 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:24\">2 Timotheo 2:24</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:42\">Mambo ya Walawi 25:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:55\">55</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:36\">1 Wafalme 11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:7\">2 Wafalme 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:20-Ps89:29\">Zaburi 89:20–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps113:1\">113:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:8-Isa41:10\">Isaya 41:8–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1-Isa42:4\">42:1–4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:19-Isa42:20\">19–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:10\">43:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:1-Isa44:5\">44:1–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:21-Isa44:22\">21–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:1-Isa49:7\">49:1–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">52:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:13-Isa53:12\">13–53:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:3\">61:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:10\">Yeremia 30:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:20-Jer33:22\">33:20–22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:26\">26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:27-Jer46:28\">46:27–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:25\">Ezekieli 28:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:23-Ezek34:24\">34:23–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:24-Ezek37:25\">37:24–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:8\">Zekaria 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:15-Matt12:21\">Mathayo 12:15–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:18\">Matendo 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:24\">2 Timotheo 2:24</a></p>",
